reader had this to say his pictures show him to be a short 
fat man malenkov spends most of his time at his office he does 
not like to go to parties or talk with strangers 
the year 1958 brought a rare product endorsement hula hoops 
are made of plastic they are a good kind of toy whirling hoops is 
good exercise for children 
